title: Room Enough | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Room Enough | Joel Osteen
description:
You can be in the center of God’s will and still face opposition. The key is to remember that God is still in control. That setback is actually a setup. He’s going to take what was meant for your harm and use it to your advantage.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
